{"key":"processedPost-6651183","value":{"id":6651183,"first":6649719,"last":6651183,"when":1173420172,"utime":"03/09/07 08:02 AM","content":"If using pf tek, be sure to keep the holes taped until ready to inoculate. If you don't, sometimes contaminants will settle on the top verm layer, and then your needle will push them through to the substrate below.<br />Always flame sterilize needles and other tools between jars.  This eliminates the possibility of cross contamination.<br />Wear gloves and wash them with alcohol after putting them on.<br />Wear a surgical mask and don't talk while working.  The spit that leaves your mouth when you talk will easily penetrate even a surgical mask.<br />Work in a small closed room with no drafts.  Use oust to sanitize the air itself, and alcohol or Lysol to sanitize surfaces.<br />As said, get your first few syringes from a reputable source.  With a bit of experience, you'll be making your own in no time.<br />Good luck to you.<br />RR","title":"Re: novice grower. I have green mold. PLEASE HELP"}}